Steps to build and run:	

Linux:

      $ git clone git@github.com:flexoid/rTracer.git
      $ cd rTracer/src
      $ cmake .
      $ make
      $ ../bin/rTracer

Windows:

   MSYS:
      $ git clone git@github.com:flexoid/rTracer.git
      $ cd rTracer/src
      $ cmake -G "MSYS Makefiles" .
      $ make
      $ ../bin/rTracer.exe

   MinGW:
      $ git clone git@github.com:flexoid/rTracer.git
      $ cd rTracer\src
      $ cmake -G "MinGW Makefiles" .
      $ mingw32-make
      $ ..\bin\rTracer.exe

